298
00:16:17,679 --> 00:16:18,559
half is flattery.

299
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:21,679
It's just that

300
00:16:25,559 --> 00:16:26,840
those words aren't directed at me,

301
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,279
but at my status.

302
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:34,679
Because

303
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:38,120
I'm the Nation's Little Sister, Yin Shanshan.

304
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:39,919
So then,

305
00:16:40,039 --> 00:16:41,159
no matter what I do,

306
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:42,720
whether I do it well

307
00:16:43,679 --> 00:16:44,360
or do it badly,

308
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,080
they'll all say

309
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:49,039
Well done!

310
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:52,720
Shanshan—

311
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,399
Call me Auntie.

312
00:17:07,119 --> 00:17:07,640
Auntie.

313
00:17:09,839 --> 00:17:10,680
They're right.

314
00:17:12,279 --> 00:17:13,319
You are beautiful.

315
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,319
You are right.

316
00:17:16,599 --> 00:17:17,480
You are the cutest.

317
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:23,519
In my heart,

318
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:25,839
you are the best

319
00:17:27,559 --> 00:17:28,319
in the whole world.

320
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:29,920
Bar none.
